OL,3,CFormer football club owner loses bid
OL,4,Cto appeal against fraud convictions
OL,6,FThe former owner of Fleetwood Town FC
OL,7,Fhas lost a bid to challenge his
OL,8,Fconvictions for multiple fraud
OL,9,Foffences at the Court of Appeal.
OL,11,FAndy Pilley, who had been the chairman
OL,12,Fand owner of the League Two side for
OL,13,F20 years until he stepped down in
OL,14,F2023, was handed a 13-year prison
OL,15,Fsentence in July that year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
